      <span class="status-text">Maintenance in progress ‚Äî back soon ‚ö°</span>
    </div>

    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="https://discord.gg/aqeBVdeu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link discord">
        üí¨ Join us on Discord
      </a>
      <a href="https://x.com/pixelsdojo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link twitter">
        üê¶ Follow us on X for updates
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="admin-hint">
      Admin? <a href="/login">Log in</a> to access the site during maintenance.
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
